parameters:
\n< Serena >"I've come quite deep... Somehow, it's
darker and chillier around here."
\n< ??? >"Who's there?!"
\n< Serena >"Hmm?"

\n< Serena >"Don't be on guard. I just happened to
come here. I heard there are valuable
herbs growing around this area."
\n< Serena >"I have no business with you."
\n< Serena >"What are you doing here?"
\n< ??? >"You don't know what this place is?"
\n< Serena >"I do not. It's my first time here."

\n< ??? >"Heh, aren't you lucky? Better off not
knowing, I say."
\n< Serena >"You're not making much sense..."

\n< ??? >"Doesn't matter, does it? Well, I'm
going to take my leave now."

\n< Serena >"Ah... Hmm? That flower in your right
hand..."

\n< Serena >"Translucent blue petals, scales that
scatter like light..."

\n< Serena >"Isn't that the Kokeshi grass... I came
looking for it."
\n< ??? >"...Hah... This? You want it?"

\n< Serena >"I need it. There's no more around here,
is there...?"

\n< ??? >"Nope. This is all of it. I picked them
all."

\n< Serena >"...Then I'll buy that flower from you
for 10G."

\n< ??? >"Huh, you'll pay money? You need it that
badly?"

\n< Serena >"To be honest, I have no personal need
or interest in it. But it's what I've
been tasked to procure."
\n< ??? >"A fellow professional, huh."
\n< Serena >"Is the amount unsatisfactory?"

\n< ??? >"Hmm-? Well... If you give me ten times
that, maybe I'll consider parting with
it?"
\n< Serena >"Understood. I'll pay it."
\n< ??? >"Hah? You know. 100G, 100G?!"

\n< ??? >"No way you'd get that much money for a
weed- picking request!"

\n< Serena >"That's true. But it's not about the
money."
\n< Serena >"Please. I'll buy it for 100G."

\n< ??? >"...Hah. Ridiculous... Just messing with
a kid, that's all."

\n< ??? >"Like someone as pint-sized as you would
have that kind of money."
\n< ??? >"Here, take it for free. There you go."
\n< Serena >"Hmm?... Really? Is that okay?"

\n< ??? >"It's like a weed. Around here, if you
leave it alone, it'll grow back in no
time."

\n< ??? >"...Really, one after another with these
people..."

\n< Serena >"I don't quite understand, but... thank
you. This will complete the request."
\n< ??? >"Hah, glad to hear it."

\n< ??? >Well then, take care and make sure you
get home safely.
\n< Serena >Ah, I will. You take care as well.
\n< ??? >...What am I even doing...

\n< ??? >Ahh, somehow everything's just becoming
so annoying.

\n< ??? >Maybe I should just quit being an
adventurer...
\n< ??? >...If only it were that easy...
